name: Face of Mankind: Fall of the Dominion
blurb: A futuristic sandbox MMO ruled by the harsh realities of human nature. You forge your own future and rise to fame.

rewards.reward: No Reward

We would like to thank you sincerely for your support in helping build this amazing sandbox multiplayer game. You will receive a SPECIAL in-game shirt for your character which will let everyone know that YOU helped this project succeed.

You will receive an EXCLUSIVE in-game Kickstarter hat for your character plus SPECIAL ACCESS to the private DEVELOPER FORUM to help us improve the game. We will share exclusive information and our undying gratitude. You will also receive a unique icon on your in-game "player file" to show others that you are an original backer. \u25cf Includes all the above rewards \u25cf
